James Mitarotonda Insider Buy Transaction
 Eastern Co (NASDAQ:EML)  29.90 -0.40 -1.32%‘s director, James Mitarotonda, invested in 1,019 shares of stock in the fabricated metal product manufacturing’s company. The reported average cost paid by James Mitarotonda per share was $16.0, for aggregate transaction sum of $16,304 US Dollars. James is trying to quietly increase his company’s share, same as he did in the last month. He obtained another 21,454 shares worth $348,912 USD. James Mitarotonda now indirectly holds 506354 shares. He also directly holds 587 shares. In total he holds a stake of 7.95%. The filing was disclosed in a filing dated October 1, 2015 with the SEC.
